The '''Municipal Commissioner of Pune''' is the chief executive officer of the [[Pune Municipal Corporation]]. The Municipal Commissioner maintains Pune, and thus has responsibilities over the sewage system, the school divisions, power companies, roads, and other aspects of local infrastructure. The commissioner is an [[Indian Administrative Service]] officer appointed by the [[Maharashtra]] state government. Shri. Kunal Kumar, is the current Municipal Commissioner of [[Pune]]<ref>{{cite news|title=Kunal Kumar named new Pune civic chief|url=http://www.sakaaltimes.com/SakaalTimesBeta/20110510/4825435414976419155.htm|accessdate=18 July 2011|newspaper=Sakaal Times|date=May 10, 2011}}</ref>
